Conditional statements:
	To make the set instructions execute only when the given condition is Truw
	Used to decide whether the code has to be executed or skip based on the given condition
	line-line(sequence)
block of code: set of instructions
	It will execute only when the condition is true

Condition: An expression that evaluates a result (True or False)
	Ex: console.log (5>6);
Methods:
	if, if-else, else, switch, Ternary operator


